sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant Batch as Adaptive Batcher
    participant Cache as Response Cache
    participant Registry as Model Registry
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lgbm/onnx)
    participant Dispatcher as Parallel Dispatcher
    participant Worker as Worker Process<br/>(multiprocessing)
    participant KafkaBroker as Kafka Broker<br/>9092/TCP

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / mTLS
    Gateway->>REST: HTTP/8080<br/>No TLS (pod-internal)
    REST->>DP: InferenceRequest
    DP->>Cache: Check cache
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>DP: Cached response
    else Cache Miss
        DP->>Batch: Queue request
        Note over Batch: Collect until max_batch_size<br/>or max_batch_time expires
        Batch->>Registry: Batched predict()
        Registry->>Runtime: Model.predict(batch)
        Runtime-->>Registry: InferenceResponse[]
        Registry-->>Batch: Batch result
        Batch-->>DP: Individual response
        DP->>Cache: Store in cache
    end
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Gateway: HTTP 200 JSON
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: ModelInfer RPC<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / mTLS
    Gateway->>GRPC: gRPC/8081<br/>No TLS (pod-internal)
    GRPC->>DP: InferenceRequest
    DP->>Registry: predict()
    Registry->>Runtime: Model.predict()
    Runtime-->>Registry: InferenceResponse
    Registry-->>DP: Result
    DP-->>GRPC: InferenceResponse
    GRPC-->>Gateway: ModelInferResponse
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over KafkaBroker,Runtime: Flow 3: Kafka Async Inference
    KafkaBroker->>REST: Kafka Consumer polls<br/>9092/TCP
    REST->>DP: InferenceRequest (from message)
    DP->>Registry: predict()
    Registry->>Runtime: Model.predict()
    Runtime-->>Registry: InferenceResponse
    Registry-->>DP: Result
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST->>KafkaBroker: Kafka Producer publishes<br/>9092/TCP

    Note over DP,Worker: Flow 4: Parallel Inference (Multi-Worker)
    DP->>Dispatcher: ParallelModel.predict()
    Dispatcher->>Worker: IPC multiprocessing.Queue
    Worker->>Runtime: Model.predict() in subprocess
    Runtime-->>Worker: Result
    Worker-->>Dispatcher: IPC multiprocessing.Queue
    Dispatcher-->>DP: asyncio.Future resolved
